1.0.0.6.name: connect20/Clorida_Taxamo
1.0.0.6.description: This module provides tax price calculation for both B2B and B2C transactions. It is a SaaS-based solution enabling digital sellers to quickly and easily comply with global taxation laws enabling real-time EU VAT product compliance with VAT calculation, evidence, invoicing, EU MOSS returns and audit services.

suggest.magento-hackathon\/magento-composer-inst: Allows to manage this package as a dependency
